quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  17,106,"And (it is) a Qur’ân which We have divided (into parts), in order that you might recite it to men at intervals. And We have revealed it by stages (in 23 years)."
  17,107,"Say (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه و سلم to them): "
  17,108,"And they say: "
  18,73,"[Mûsâ (Moses)] said: ",footnotes:1:{18:73}
  18,74,"Then they both proceeded, till they met a boy, and he (Khidr) killed him. Mûsâ (Moses) said: "
  18,75,"(Khidr) said: "
  19,34,"Such is ‘Îsâ (Jesus), son of Maryam (Mary). (It is) a statement of truth, about which they doubt (or dispute)."
  19,35,"It befits not (the Majesty of) Allâh that He should beget a son [this refers to the slander of Christians against Allâh, by saying that ‘Îsâ (Jesus) is the son of Allâh]. Glorified (and Exalted) be He (above all that they associate with Him). When He decrees a thing, He only says to it: ",footnotes:1:{19:35} See the footnote of (Verse 2:116).
  19,36,"[‘Îsâ (Jesus) said]: "
  20,16,"",footnotes:1:{20:16} See the footnote of (Verse 19:59)
  20,17,""
  20,18,"He said: "